skdetail:

Invocation Name: fun art quiz
des:
Alexa quizzes you on your general art knowledge. Answer these 15 art questions and see if you can put your art knowledge to the test.
This art trivia quiz by Fabulous Masterpieces is suitable for the whole family. 
Fabulous Masterpieces specialises in hand painting fine art replicas of your favourite paintings. To see some of our artwork visit www.fabulousmasterpieces.co.uk
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
